data.title: St. John the Baptist
data.meta_description: Building up the Catholic Faith of children so that families may be a Witness to Christ's Divine Love! Serving Draper, Sandy, and the greater Salt Lake City area. Join us for Mass, confession, adoration, religious education, and more!
